ksdk:manifest.name: SDK version 2.4.2 package for EVKB-IMXRT1050 board
ksdk:manifest.brief: This is SDK version 2.4.2 manifest file. It describes the content of the SDK version 2.4.2 package for EVKB-IMXRT1050 board and additional settings for tools that support SDK version 2.4.2

board.name: EVKB-IMXRT1050
board.description: IMXRT1050-EVKB: EVK Development Platform for i.MX MIMXRT1052 and MIMXRT1051 MCUs

specific.content: The NXP IMXRT1050-EVKB is a development board for the i.MX MIMXRT1052 and MIMXRT1051 600 MHz 32-bit ARM® Cortex®-M7 MCUs

board.name: EVKB-IMXRT1050-AGM01
board.description: Sensor Toolbox Development Platform for FXAS21002C and FXOS8700C 9-Axis Solution

specific.content:
Demonstration Custom Kit (FRDM-STBC-AGM01 Sensor Shield Development Board with EVKB-IMXRT1050 Board):
  • Enables quick and easy visualization of 9-Axis (3 Axis Gyroscope + 6-Axis E-compass) sensor data and results.

board.name: EVKB-IMXRT1050-OM13588
board.description: USB Type-C Shield Board for Kinetis Freedom Board

specific.content: The USB Type-C shield board combined with a Kinetis Power Delivery SDK allows a system designer to tether a USB Type-C connector to any Kinetis development platform.

device.name: MIMXRT1052
device.description: MIMXRT1052: i.MX® MIMXRT1052 600MHz, 512KB SRAM Microcontrollers (MCUs) based on ARM® Cortex®-M7 Core

specific.content: The MIMXRT1052 are ARM Cortex-M7 based microcontrollers for embedded applications.
